metadata.name: W3P TIER 1 #1
metadata.description: An invite-only global private community of Web 3 and Metaverse practitioners, business owners and advisors actively engaged in the space. Our members comprise founders, investors, end-users and consultants with cross-industry experience in business and industry from Web 2 who have transitioned to Web 3. W3P Membership is open to beginners, intermediaries and experts committed to growth, leadership and delivering great innovation and outcomes for clients, partners and stakeholders. Token ownership does not guarantee membership. As an invite-only network, access to membership is by nomination and voting. Holders are welcome to buy, sell or gift our tokens to like-minded people.
